<h2>HIST 119: <strong>The Civil War and Reconstruction Era, 1845-1877 </strong></h2>
<table id="lectureHeader" summary="lecture header" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
	<tr>
		<td width="510" nowrap="nowrap">
			<span id="lectureNum">Lecture 18 - </span>
			<span id="lectureName">"War So Terrible": Why the Union Won and the Confederacy <div id="secondHeaderLine">Lost at Home and Abroad</div></span></td>
		<td width="248" id="lectureNav" nowrap="nowrap">
